### **Entity Type Selection Guidelines**

#### **For ecoNET-300 Integration:**
- **Binary sensor** - Pump status, fan status, alarm status
  - **Device Classes**: `RUNNING` (pumps, fans), `PROBLEM` (alarms), `CONNECTIVITY` (network status)
  - **Properties**: `is_on` (required boolean), `device_class` (optional)
  - **Reference**: [Binary Sensor Documentation](https://developers.home-assistant.io/docs/core/entity/binary-sensor)
- **Sensor** - Temperature readings, alarm codes, version info
- **Number** - Temperature setpoints, configuration values
- **Switch** - Boiler ON/OFF control
- **Select** - Operation modes, season modes
- **Climate** - Advanced HVAC control (if applicable)
- **Update** - Firmware updates (if available)

